snippet.title: Waddle Knight Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for the Kirby fan games Waddle Knight and the Waddle Knight 2 Demo.

Check out the first Waddle Knight, it's fully completed!
https://waddledev.itch.io/waddle-knight
https://gamejolt.com/games/waddleknight/837356

Also, check out the demo for Waddle Knight 2, which has over 25 bosses!
https://waddledev.itch.io/waddle-knight-2
https://gamejolt.com/games/waddleknight2/872303
